=== "Python"
    ```python
    def dfs(i):
        if mem[i] != -1:
            return mem[i]
        ret = 1
        for j in range(1, i):
            if a[j] < a[i]:
                ret = max(ret, dfs(j) + 1)
        mem[i] = ret
